    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a mysterious world on a quest for a <strong>lost civilization</strong>. Solve puzzles and try to prevent <strong>disaster</strong> from unfolding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nyria</strong>, a young <strong>archaeologist</strong> and <strong>adventurer</strong>, is searching for a way to save her world from a <strong>dire fate</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To do so, she places her hopes in exploring the ruins of an <strong>ancient and mysterious civilization</strong> that vanished long ago.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the <strong>Depths of the Ruins,</strong> she encounters mysterious entities and follows in the footsteps of explorers who came before her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She gradually uncovers numerous Secrets of the <strong>Forgotten Past</strong> and comes to understand that these ruins are, in fact, connected to the very fabric of <strong>Space and Time</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the only one capable of <strong>unraveling and solving the threads of destiny</strong>, Nyria unexpectedly finds herself carrying a burden far heavier than she ever imagined…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras/43bccba95106d323837879582221a71d.avif?t=1763746450\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras_big/43bccba95106d323837879582221a71d.avif?t=1763746450 width=800 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the <strong>traps</strong> protecting the ruins and <strong>help the inhabitants</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras/319e30fe579d4c25208c47219b623773.avif?t=1763746450\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras_big/319e30fe579d4c25208c47219b623773.avif?t=1763746450 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Energy</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manipulate</strong> the energy of <strong>Generators</strong> to activate or deactivate other objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras/caaec2662c09d314ffc64be5712682b6.poster.avif?t=1763746450\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras/caaec2662c09d314ffc64be5712682b6.webm?t=1763746450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras/caaec2662c09d314ffc64be5712682b6.mp4?t=1763746450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Switches &amp; Blocks</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move <strong>energy-charged</strong> blocks to activate <strong>mechanisms within the ruins</strong> and carve your path forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras/5ffc55c00a5e7a3aa17f9657b108a109.poster.avif?t=1763746450\" width=718 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras/5ffc55c00a5e7a3aa17f9657b108a109.webm?t=1763746450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402220/extras/5ffc55c00a5e7a3aa17f9657b108a109.mp4?t=1763746450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself by solving puzzles in an exciting adventure lasting 7 to 9 hours.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the strange inhabitants of the ruins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re new to puzzles or an experienced player, <i>Monolith's Dreamers</i> offers levels tailored to every type of player.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The controls are simplified to ensure easy handling and provide a puzzle-focused experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About Us :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are an independent video game studio made up of a team of passionate developers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We love retro games and pixel art, and we aim to share our passion with players through unique and captivating experiences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our ambition is to create quality content for players, blending traditional and innovative experiences in small to mid-budget games.</p>",
